{
  "name": "RPlog_Han_s_Rescue",
  "title": "The Rescue of Han Solo on Athaniss",
  "summary": "On the planet Athaniss, the Empire stages a public show-trial and execution of Han Solo, presided over by Judge Laurence Dante and overseen by Moff Morrison Van Sen and Director Petra Doom. Disguised among the crowd, Luke Skywalker leads a New Republic rescue team that includes Leia, the Jedi apprentices Ai'kani and Sabrina, and soldiers Stanley and Rook, while the astromech R2-D2 detonates a diversionary bomb at a munitions facility. As the trial turns to a beating, Luke leaps onto the gallows, severs Petra's blaster, and frees Han amid a chaotic firefight against stormtroopers and the airborne Imperial agent Danik Kreldin. Sabrina commandeers a luxury speeder and extracts the battered Han along with the rest of the team, though Rook is gravely wounded by grenade fire before being pulled aboard. The rescue succeeds and the New Republic party escapes, leaving Petra to brace for her Master's wrath over the failed execution.",
